navigate_back.doc_string: Navigates to the previous commit based on commit visit history.

navigate_forward.doc_string: Navigates to the next commit based on commit visit history.

navigate_to_commit_message.doc_string: Brings the focus to the commit message dialog.

navigate_to_context_commit.doc_string: Navigates to the commit referenced (through it's hash) in the commit message.

args.name: commit
args.doc_string: The hash of the commit you want to navigate to. Passing in a non existent commit hash will throw an error dialog.

navigate_to_tag.doc_string: Navigates to the specific commit that has the referenced tag.

navigate_to_child.doc_string: Navigates to the child commit of the currently focussed commit.

navigate_to_parent.doc_string: Navigates to the parent commit of the currently focussed commit.

next_file_tab.doc_string: Navigates to the next file tab.

next_tab.doc_string: Navigates to the next repository tab.

new_window.doc_string: Opens a new window for cloning a new repository, opening an existing repository or creating a new repository.
